body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Depot. My name is Gabriel Allen. May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Elizabeth. Can you please provide the last four digits of your social security number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's three two zero zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you. Can you also confirm your date of birth in the format day, month, year?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, it's zero five, zero three, one nine nine zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for verifying that, Elizabeth. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, I think that's all. Thank you.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Elizabeth. Have a great day!
